##Shenzhen will completely cancel the re-work and re-production approval, re-work and re-check first

Function introduction, the interface news is China has the influence original financial and economic new media, only serves the independent thinking crowd

Image: Visual China

REPORTER: Liang Zhou

“

For those enterprises that have reached the standard of resuming production and work, they can now resume production and work without waiting for examination or approval.

”

“

For those enterprises that have reached the standard of resuming production and work, they can now resume production and work without waiting for examination or approval.

”

On February 20,2020, interface news learned from the Office of the COVID-19 that Shenzhen will completely cancel the verification and approval of the record of the resumption of work in enterprises, and instead commit to record-keeping by enterprises.

At present, the epidemic prevention and control of NCP has entered a critical period, and the work of resuming production and returning to work is also being carried out. On February 3, the Office of the COVID-19 in Shenzhen issued a notice on the implementation of the reporting system for enterprises returning to work after February 9 to implement the reporting system. Enterprises need to meet the prevention and control mechanism in place, staff investigation in place, facilities and materials in place, internal management in place and so on.

At that time, the city of Shenzhen also requested that the system of reporting and reviewing the resumption of production and work be implemented. All kinds of enterprises in the city should report back to the epidemic prevention and control headquarters in their respective jurisdictions at least 5 days (natural days) before the commencement of work, provided that the above-mentioned conditions are met, to submit the return to production, return to work record form, epidemic prevention and control commitment.

The first imported case of new coronary pneumonia was confirmed in Shenzhen on January 19. As of 2400 hours on February 19,416 confirmed cases of new coronary pneumonia had been reported in Shenzhen. There were no new confirmed cases in the city on February 19. At present, 10 severe cases, 10 critical cases, 2 deaths, a total of 182 discharged from the hospital. 287 close contacts are under medical observation.

Now, as the situation of epidemic prevention and control changes, Shenzhen regulation of the resumption of production and resumption of work policies also began to adjust. On February 20, a screenshot of Shenzhen's resumption of production and work spread on the Internet. The screenshot showed that, "The municipal government will completely cancel the verification and approval of the re-work of enterprises for the record-keeping, and the re-work of enterprises for the record-keeping commitment will be sufficient. Enterprises that have not yet returned to work should, in light of their actual conditions, resume work as soon as possible under the premise of carrying out the prevention, control and management of the epidemic situation. "

The screenshot also shows that the quarantine measures adopted by the Shenzhen municipal government for people returning to Shenzhen from other places have also changed, "It will be adjusted to 1 + 1[ in Hubei and Wenzhou in Zhejiang ] . At present, people in these two areas will be classified and quarantined, and the remaining areas will be completely lifted. "

In response, an office worker of the COVID-19 headquarters for the prevention and control of pneumonia infection in Shenzhen told the interface news that it is true that Shenzhen has cancelled the verification and approval of the re-work of enterprises for record keeping and has changed the commitment to record keeping by enterprises, the document is likely to be officially released in the next day or two.

Headquarters office staff said that for enterprises that meet the standards for resuming production and work, they can now first register with government departments, according to the requirements of the epidemic prevention measures can resume production and work. After the resumption of production and resumption of work, government departments or street workers will visit at any time to check whether the epidemic prevention work in place.

Regarding the quarantine measures for people returning to Shenzhen from other places, the staff member said that after the new policy was issued, people returning to Shenzhen from Hubei Province and Wenzhou from Zhejiang Province would still need to be isolated for observation for 14 days, "If they have the conditions to be isolated at home and do not have a fever or other special circumstances that require medical observation, they can be isolated at home. Those returning to Shenzhen from areas other than Wenzhou in Hubei and Zhejiang, who do not have fever or other special circumstances, can return to work directly."

Staff also pointed out that after the resumption of work, if the health of employees, the need for timely reporting to the community, streets, "The isolation of the quarantine, the hospital should be sent to the hospital for examination, so the requirement for enterprises to measure the body temperature of employees every day, timely grasp their physical condition, physical abnormalities to deal with quickly, can not delay. "

Interface News noted that in recent days, a number of districts in Shenzhen City has launched the resumption of work without the need for approval of the policy. According to a report by the Southern Metropolis Daily, the Luohu district of Shenzhen City stipulates that in addition to tourism and leisure, Saunas and massages, movies and TV shows, video games, bars, Internet cafes and other enterprises with high risk of personnel gathering, after reaching the rework standard and submitting the rework record form of the enterprise and the epidemic prevention and control commitment of the enterprise, the rework can be resumed without waiting for examination or approval.

In Nanshan district, Shenzhen, companies that are not part of the entertainment industry such as cinemas, Karaoke bars, conferences and exhibitions, where people are relatively concentrated and the working environment is relatively closed, will be allowed to resume work, southern Plus reported. After the enterprise first returns to work, the government will organize the staff to go to the House for verification. If the company is found to belong to the type of enterprise that has suspended the start of work, or fails to meet the requirements for prevention and control, it will be investigated and dealt with according to law.

In addition, outside Shenzhen, a number of regions have also made adjustments to the resumption process. For example, Jiangmen of Guangdong has completely abolished the procedures for examination and approval and preparation for enterprises to resume work and production, and enterprises do not need approval for resuming work and production, nor do they need to sign an undertaking; In Ningbo, Zhejiang Province, the approval procedures for the resumption of work and production of various enterprises and construction projects due to epidemic prevention and control were cancelled, and the resumption of work and production was replaced by the reporting system.
